name: Peonies Cushion 45cm
description:
The classic ‘Peonies’ Cushion is a garden beauty.

Extra special care has been taken during the production of this Limited Edition piece.

- Designed and made in Australia 
- Digitally printed with water based inks (without heavy duty dyes & chemicals)
- Size: 45 x 45cm
- Includes a quality 100% feather insert
- Belgium cotton/ linen blend fabric
- 100% cotton fringe trim and an invisible zipper

This beauty has its own natural charm. As such, there may be slight variations (slubs and neps) in the natural fabric making each piece unique. 

To keep your cushion in royal condition, please follow the care instructions. Gently hand wash reverse cushion cover in warm 
water with a gentle laundry liquid detergent. Please do not bleach, tumble dry or dry clean. Warm Iron only.

FREE SHIPPING WITHIN AUSTRALIA!

PRE-ORDER FOR A 2-3 WEEK DELIVERY

Designed by Natala Stuetz in Brisbane, Australia. © 2013 Ma and Grandy

A4 size: 29.7 x 21 cm

Each artwork is signed on the back by designer Natala Stuetz.

FREE SHIPPING WITHIN AUSTRALIA!

A3 size available upon request. Send us an email at info@maandgrandy.com
